            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-1007] When A URL is redirected, there is no easy way to encode the new url before HC tries to execute it/</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1007</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>When you implement your custom RedirectHandler, there is no easy way to encode the new URL being redirected to.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
